# =============================================================================
# Core Data Engine - Sensor Configuration
# =============================================================================
# This file documents all available environment variables for configuring
# the sensor modules. All variables are optional - the system will use
# sensible defaults if not provided.
#
# Configuration can also be provided programmatically via SensorConfig.
# See src/core/config/sensorConfig.ts for details.
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Weather API Configuration
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OpenWeatherMap API key for current weather and forecast data.
# Get your free API key at: https://openweathermap.org/api
#
# Required for: Weather-based XP modifiers (storm bonus, night bonus, etc.)
WEATHER_API_KEY=your_openweathermap_api_key_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Steam Integration
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Steam Web API key for game detection and metadata.
# Get your API key at: https://steamcommunity.com/dev/apikey
#
# Required for: Gaming-based XP modifiers (RPG bonus, multiplayer bonus, etc.)
STEAM_API_KEY=your_steam_api_key_here

# Optional: Your 64-bit Steam ID. If not provided, you'll need to pass it
# when calling authenticate() on GamingPlatformSensors.
# Find your Steam ID at: https://steamid.io/
STEAM_USER_ID=your_64bit_steam_id_here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# XP Modifier Configuration (Optional)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Maximum XP modifier multiplier (default: 3.0)
# Controls the maximum bonus XP that can be earned from environmental and
# gaming factors combined. Set to 1.0 to disable all bonuses, or higher
# to allow more extreme multipliers.
# XP_MAX_MODIFIER=3.0

# =============================================================================
# Configuration Examples
# =============================================================================
#
# Minimal setup (weather + Steam gaming):
#   WEATHER_API_KEY=abc123
#   STEAM_API_KEY=def456
#   STEAM_USER_ID=76561198012345678
#
# Development/testing (disable XP bonuses):
#   XP_MAX_MODIFIER=1.0
#
# =============================================================================
# See src/core/config/sensorConfig.ts for programmatic configuration options
# and complete default values for all sensors.
# =============================================================================
